"{\"uid\": \"forbes.com-sites-emmawoollacott-2024-07-11-beware-of-scam-ticket-websites-olympics-fans-warned\", \"noun_phrases\": [{\"sentence\": \"ByEmma Woollacott, Senior Contributor.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 39, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7, \"end\": 17, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Martin_Woollacott\", \"score\": 0.9999998679732104, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Woollacott\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q1930187\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Martin_Woollacott\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Martin_Woollacott\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Senior Contributor\", \"from\": 19, \"to\": 37}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As the Paris Summer Olympics approach, fans are being advised to keep a careful eye out for scams targeting their cash and their data.\", \"from\": 41, \"to\": 175, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Paris Summer Olympics approach\", \"from\": 44, \"to\": 78}, {\"ngram\": \"fans\", \"from\": 80, \"to\": 84}, {\"ngram\": \"a careful eye\", \"from\": 111, \"to\": 124}, {\"ngram\": \"scams\", \"from\": 133, \"to\": 138}, {\"ngram\": \"their cash\", \"from\": 149, \"to\": 159}, {\"ngram\": \"their data\", \"from\": 164, \"to\": 174}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Fake ticket websites are rife, with the Olympics Committee recently warning that fraudsters are claiming to offer free tickets to the opening ceremony of the 2024 Paralympic Games for just the cost of postage.\", \"from\": 177, \"to\": 386, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Fake ticket websites\", \"from\": 177, \"to\": 197}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics Committee\", \"from\": 213, \"to\": 235}, {\"ngram\": \"fraudsters\", \"from\": 258, \"to\": 268}, {\"ngram\": \"free tickets\", \"from\": 291, \"to\": 303}, {\"ngram\": \"the opening ceremony\", \"from\": 307, \"to\": 327}, {\"ngram\": \"the 2024 Paralympic Games\", \"from\": 331, \"to\": 356}, {\"ngram\": \"just the cost\", \"from\": 361, \"to\": 374}, {\"ngram\": \"postage\", \"from\": 378, \"to\": 385}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Researchers at security firm Kaspersky say that numerous scam websites are offering tickets for Olympic competitions at \\\"exclusive\\\" prices, or claiming to have seats for sold-out events.\", \"from\": 388, \"to\": 574, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 417, \"end\": 426, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kaspersky_Lab\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.271835787754568e-14, \"text\": \"Kaspersky\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kaspersky_Lab\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kaspersky_Lab\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Researchers\", \"from\": 388, \"to\": 399}, {\"ngram\": \"security firm\", \"from\": 403, \"to\": 416}, {\"ngram\": \"numerous scam websites\", \"from\": 436, \"to\": 458}, {\"ngram\": \"tickets\", \"from\": 472, \"to\": 479}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympic competitions\", \"from\": 484, \"to\": 504}, {\"ngram\": \"\\\"exclusive\\\" prices\", \"from\": 508, \"to\": 526}, {\"ngram\": \"seats\", \"from\": 548, \"to\": 553}, {\"ngram\": \"sold-out events\", \"from\": 558, \"to\": 573}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"This well-tested yet effective fraudulent scheme has resurfaced during many Olympic seasons, and Kaspersky's experts expect such websites to proliferate during Paris 2024,\\\" warns the firm.\", \"from\": 576, \"to\": 765, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 674, \"end\": 683, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kaspersky_Lab\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.271835787754568e-14, \"text\": \"Kaspersky\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kaspersky_Lab\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kaspersky_Lab\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"This well-tested yet effective fraudulent scheme\", \"from\": 577, \"to\": 625}, {\"ngram\": \"many Olympic seasons\", \"from\": 648, \"to\": 668}, {\"ngram\": \"such websites\", \"from\": 701, \"to\": 714}, {\"ngram\": \"Paris\", \"from\": 737, \"to\": 742}, {\"ngram\": \"the firm\", \"from\": 756, \"to\": 764}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"In this scenario, users fill out a data form and transfer both their personal information and money to scammers.\", \"from\": 766, \"to\": 879, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this scenario\", \"from\": 770, \"to\": 783}, {\"ngram\": \"users\", \"from\": 785, \"to\": 790}, {\"ngram\": \"a data form\", \"from\": 800, \"to\": 811}, {\"ngram\": \"both their personal information\", \"from\": 825, \"to\": 856}, {\"ngram\": \"money\", \"from\": 861, \"to\": 866}, {\"ngram\": \"scammers\", \"from\": 870, \"to\": 878}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As a result, they may receive invalid tickets or, more likely, nothing at all, leading to financial loss and their data being sold on Dark Web forums.\\\"\", \"from\": 880, \"to\": 1031, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1014, \"end\": 1022, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dark_web\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.753513828818031e-51, \"text\": \"Dark Web\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dark_web\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dark_web\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a result\", \"from\": 883, \"to\": 891}, {\"ngram\": \"invalid tickets\", \"from\": 910, \"to\": 925}, {\"ngram\": \"nothing\", \"from\": 943, \"to\": 950}, {\"ngram\": \"financial loss\", \"from\": 970, \"to\": 984}, {\"ngram\": \"their data\", \"from\": 989, \"to\": 999}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And anyone can fall for such scams, with even the family of one Olympic swimmer, Matt Richards, losing \\u00a32,500 ($3,225) through just this type of fraud.\", \"from\": 1033, \"to\": 1184, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1114, \"end\": 1127, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Matt_Richards_(footballer,_born_1984)\", \"score\": 0.8167390230816501, \"rank\": 0.2243767313019458, \"text\": \"Matt Richards\", \"types\": [\"Q937857\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Matt_Richards_(footballer,_born_1984)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Matt_Richards_(footballer,_born_1984)\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"anyone\", \"from\": 1037, \"to\": 1043}, {\"ngram\": \"such scams\", \"from\": 1057, \"to\": 1067}, {\"ngram\": \"even the family\", \"from\": 1074, \"to\": 1089}, {\"ngram\": \"one Olympic swimmer\", \"from\": 1093, \"to\": 1112}, {\"ngram\": \"just this type\", \"from\": 1160, \"to\": 1174}, {\"ngram\": \"fraud\", \"from\": 1178, \"to\": 1183}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Some of these fake websites are highly prominent: one, identified by security firm Proofpoint, was listed as the second sponsored search result on Google-after only the official website-when searching for \\\"Paris 2024 tickets.\\\"\", \"from\": 1186, \"to\": 1412, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1269, \"end\": 1279, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Proofpoint,_Inc.\", \"score\": 0.9351960225648592, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Proofpoint\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Proofpoint,_Inc.\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Proofpoint,_Inc.\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"these fake websites\", \"from\": 1194, \"to\": 1213}, {\"ngram\": \"the second sponsored search result\", \"from\": 1295, \"to\": 1329}, {\"ngram\": \"the official website\", \"from\": 1351, \"to\": 1371}, {\"ngram\": \"Paris 2024 tickets\", \"from\": 1392, \"to\": 1410}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Unsuspecting users likely clicked on the website because it appeared to be a legitimate entity that specialized in the sale of Olympic tickets.\", \"from\": 1414, \"to\": 1558, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Unsuspecting users\", \"from\": 1415, \"to\": 1433}, {\"ngram\": \"the website\", \"from\": 1452, \"to\": 1463}, {\"ngram\": \"a legitimate entity\", \"from\": 1490, \"to\": 1509}, {\"ngram\": \"the sale\", \"from\": 1530, \"to\": 1538}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympic tickets\", \"from\": 1542, \"to\": 1557}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The website's placement on the search engine under the official Paris Olympics ticket site could have further added to its legitimacy, convincing users that they were an authorized and safe source,\\\" the researchers say.\", \"from\": 1559, \"to\": 1778, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1623, \"end\": 1637, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Paris Olympics\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The website's placement\", \"from\": 1559, \"to\": 1582}, {\"ngram\": \"the search engine\", \"from\": 1586, \"to\": 1603}, {\"ngram\": \"its legitimacy\", \"from\": 1678, \"to\": 1692}, {\"ngram\": \"users\", \"from\": 1705, \"to\": 1710}, {\"ngram\": \"an authorized and safe source\", \"from\": 1726, \"to\": 1755}, {\"ngram\": \"the researchers\", \"from\": 1758, \"to\": 1773}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"While this specific domain should no longer be active, we expect other bad actors to take advantage of the event and create new fraudulent Olympics-related websites.\\\"\", \"from\": 1779, \"to\": 1946, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this specific domain\", \"from\": 1786, \"to\": 1806}, {\"ngram\": \"other bad actors\", \"from\": 1845, \"to\": 1861}, {\"ngram\": \"advantage\", \"from\": 1870, \"to\": 1879}, {\"ngram\": \"the event\", \"from\": 1883, \"to\": 1892}, {\"ngram\": \"new fraudulent Olympics-related websites\", \"from\": 1904, \"to\": 1944}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The French Gendarmerie Nationale has identified 338 fraudulent Olympics ticketing websites.\", \"from\": 1948, \"to\": 2039, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1952, \"end\": 1970, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Gendarmerie\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"French Gendarmerie\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Gendarmerie\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Gendarmerie\"}, {\"begin\": 1959, \"end\": 1980, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Gendarmerie\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.5056630120826371e-18, \"text\": \"Gendarmerie Nationale\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Gendarmerie\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Gendarmerie\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"338 fraudulent Olympics\", \"from\": 1996, \"to\": 2019}, {\"ngram\": \"websites\", \"from\": 2030, \"to\": 2038}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Of these, 51 have now been shut down, with 140 receiving formal notices from law enforcement-but many more remain.\", \"from\": 2040, \"to\": 2154, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"formal notices\", \"from\": 2097, \"to\": 2111}, {\"ngram\": \"law enforcement\", \"from\": 2117, \"to\": 2132}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Meanwhile, according to Kaspersky, scammers are also posing as corporations offering ticket giveaways, with one fraudulent page impersonating a French bank promising a chance to win tickets.\", \"from\": 2156, \"to\": 2346, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2180, \"end\": 2189, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kaspersky_Lab\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.271835787754568e-14, \"text\": \"Kaspersky\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kaspersky_Lab\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kaspersky_Lab\"}, {\"begin\": 2300, \"end\": 2306, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9866142107230739, \"rank\": 0.01266430077485274, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"scammers\", \"from\": 2191, \"to\": 2199}, {\"ngram\": \"corporations\", \"from\": 2219, \"to\": 2231}, {\"ngram\": \"ticket giveaways\", \"from\": 2241, \"to\": 2257}, {\"ngram\": \"one fraudulent page\", \"from\": 2264, \"to\": 2283}, {\"ngram\": \"a chance\", \"from\": 2322, \"to\": 2330}, {\"ngram\": \"tickets\", \"from\": 2338, \"to\": 2345}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Employees are encouraged to fill out a form with their personal details, including internet account login credentials and passwords-potentially allowing the fraudsters to infiltrate corporate networks.\", \"from\": 2348, \"to\": 2549, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Employees\", \"from\": 2348, \"to\": 2357}, {\"ngram\": \"a form\", \"from\": 2385, \"to\": 2391}, {\"ngram\": \"their personal details\", \"from\": 2397, \"to\": 2419}, {\"ngram\": \"internet account login credentials\", \"from\": 2431, \"to\": 2465}, {\"ngram\": \"passwords\", \"from\": 2470, \"to\": 2479}, {\"ngram\": \"the fraudsters\", \"from\": 2501, \"to\": 2515}, {\"ngram\": \"corporate networks\", \"from\": 2530, \"to\": 2548}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And in another scam, fraudsters have set up phishing websites offering a free 48GB data package for all phone networks, again after providing personal information such as phone numbers and payment details.\", \"from\": 2551, \"to\": 2756, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"another scam\", \"from\": 2558, \"to\": 2570}, {\"ngram\": \"fraudsters\", \"from\": 2572, \"to\": 2582}, {\"ngram\": \"websites\", \"from\": 2604, \"to\": 2612}, {\"ngram\": \"a free 48GB data package\", \"from\": 2622, \"to\": 2646}, {\"ngram\": \"all phone networks\", \"from\": 2651, \"to\": 2669}, {\"ngram\": \"personal information\", \"from\": 2693, \"to\": 2713}, {\"ngram\": \"phone numbers\", \"from\": 2722, \"to\": 2735}, {\"ngram\": \"payment details\", \"from\": 2740, \"to\": 2755}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"During major events like the Olympics, the sheer volume of offers can be overwhelming and deceptive,\\\" says Anton Yatsenko, security expert at Kaspersky.\", \"from\": 2758, \"to\": 2911, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2901, \"end\": 2910, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kaspersky_Lab\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.271835787754568e-14, \"text\": \"Kaspersky\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kaspersky_Lab\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kaspersky_Lab\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"major events\", \"from\": 2766, \"to\": 2778}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 2784, \"to\": 2796}, {\"ngram\": \"the sheer volume\", \"from\": 2798, \"to\": 2814}, {\"ngram\": \"offers\", \"from\": 2818, \"to\": 2824}, {\"ngram\": \"Anton Yatsenko\", \"from\": 2866, \"to\": 2880}, {\"ngram\": \"security expert\", \"from\": 2882, \"to\": 2897}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Scammers prey on the excitement and urgency people feel, making it crucial to approach every offer with a healthy dose of skepticism,\\\" Yatsenko adds.\", \"from\": 2913, \"to\": 3063, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Scammers prey\", \"from\": 2914, \"to\": 2927}, {\"ngram\": \"the excitement and urgency people\", \"from\": 2931, \"to\": 2964}, {\"ngram\": \"every offer\", \"from\": 3001, \"to\": 3012}, {\"ngram\": \"a healthy dose\", \"from\": 3018, \"to\": 3032}, {\"ngram\": \"skepticism\", \"from\": 3036, \"to\": 3046}, {\"ngram\": \"Yatsenko\", \"from\": 3049, \"to\": 3057}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Remember, if something seems too good to be true, it probably is.\\\"\", \"from\": 3064, \"to\": 3131, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 3078, \"to\": 3087}]}]}"